properties.areaDesc: Chesapeake Bay from Little Creek VA to Cape Henry VA including the Chesapeake Bay Bridge Tunnel; Chesapeake Bay from Windmill Point to New Point Comfort VA; Chesapeake Bay from New Point Comfort to Little Creek VA; James River from James River Bridge to Hampton Roads Bridge-Tunnel
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 22 at 10:06AM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
Observations have shown that north to northeast winds are gusting
to around 20 knots at near-surface locations across the Lower
Chesapeake Bay and Lower James River. A few 25 knot gusts are
occurring at elevated sites. Expect these gusts to continue
through the early afternoon before diminishing.

EI

NWSheadline: GUSTY NORTH TO NORTHEAST WINDS ON THE LOWER CHESAPEAKE BAY AND LOWER JAMES RIVER
